&lt;figure&gt;
&lt;img alt="물물교환은 아니지만 이건 꼭!" src="https://game.donga.com/media/__sized__/images/2025/4/14/2be6513748c649ae-thumbnail-1920x1080-70.jpg"/&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;
