&lt;figure&gt;
&lt;img alt="2연속 장갑은 좀 그렇잖아요 촌장님" src="https://game.donga.com/media/__sized__/images/2025/4/14/4ee3bac6e6fa4668-thumbnail-1920x1080-70.jpg"/&gt;
